        <source>isRetrospective(): Boolean;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
16 Feb 2024 navhl20 ChangeRequest 62418: EUP | Retrospective Operations - [54177.040] - Road Release

*/

vars

